    <item>
      <title>经合组织警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-s-trade-wars-tip-world-to-slower-growth-faster-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织说，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的积极贸易政策突然使世界迈向了增长速度较慢和通货膨胀率更高的道路，如果紧张局势升级，这可能会使世界越来越恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-s-trade-wars-tip-world-to-slower-growth-faster-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲汽油价格在特朗普 - 普京在停火方面的谈判之前流失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/european-gas-prices-slip-ahead-of-trump-putin-talks-on-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格下跌，随着天气预报的温暖和计划在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普和俄罗斯领导人弗拉基米尔·普京之间的谈判似乎增强了该地区供应余额的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/european-gas-prices-slip-ahead-of-trump-putin-talks-on-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 08:16:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
